nodes.text: Izzat was a male Twi'lek involved in the murder of Kaine Paulsen. Izzat was later killed in reprisal by Paulsen's son Drake Paulsen and his associates, Nikaede Celso, Thaddeus Ross and Tait Ransom. At the moment of his death, Izzat was working for the Galactic Empire and, as a result, the Empire offered high bounties for the heads of Izzat's murderers.
